{"pageid":29918,"pagename":"Kharid Scorpion","title":"Kharid Scorpion","displaytitle":"Kharid Scorpion","revid":14260998,"redirects":["Kharidian scorpion","Kharid scorpion"],"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"kartographer_frames","value":1},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"Kharid_Scorpion.png"},{"name":"description","value":"Kharid Scorpions are a rare species of scorpion native to the Kharidian Desert. They play a prominent role in the Scorpion Catcher quest, during which players must capture three that escaped from the wizard Thormac. Players can catch them during the Scorpion Catcher with a scorpion cage. Locations are as follows:"}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"noexcerpt noprint nomobile navigation-not-searchable rs-external-header-links\" style=\"display:none\"><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rs\" data-text=\"RuneScape\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on Kharid Scorpion.\" data-site=\"rs\">The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://runescape.wiki/w/Kharid_Scorpion\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"rsw:Kharid Scorpion\">rsw:Kharid Scorpion</a></span><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rsc\" data-text=\"CS\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Classic Wiki also has an article on Kharid Scorpion.\" data-site=\"rsc\">The RuneScape Classic Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://classic.runescape.wiki/w/Kharid_Scorpion\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"classicrsw:Kharid Scorpion\">classicrsw:Kharid Scorpion</a></span></div>\n<table class=\"infobox no-parenthesis-style infobox-npc\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-header\">Kharid Scorpion</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-full-width-content\"><a href=\"/w/File:Kharid_Scorpion.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Kharid Scorpion.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Kharid_Scorpion.png/250px-Kharid_Scorpion.png?a6456\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"250\" height=\"221\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Kharid_Scorpion.png/375px-Kharid_Scorpion.png?a6456 1.5x, /images/thumb/Kharid_Scorpion.png/500px-Kharid_Scorpion.png?a6456 2x\" data-file-width=\"923\" data-file-height=\"815\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\">Released</th><td colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/w/25_March\" title=\"25 March\">25 March</a> <a href=\"/w/2002\" title=\"2002\">2002</a> (<a href=\"/w/Update:Latest_RuneScape_News_(25_March_2002)\" title=\"Update:Latest RuneScape News (25 March 2002)\">Update</a>)</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/w/Members\" title=\"Members\">Members</a></th><td colspan=\"12\">No</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/w/Races\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Races\">Race</a></th><td colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/w/Scorpion\" title=\"Scorpion\">Scorpion</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/w/Locations\" title=\"Locations\">Location</a></th><td colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/w/Edgeville_Monastery\" title=\"Edgeville Monastery\">Edgeville Monastery</a>, <a href=\"/w/Barbarian_Outpost\" title=\"Barbarian Outpost\">Barbarian Outpost</a>, <a href=\"/w/Taverley_Dungeon\" title=\"Taverley Dungeon\">Taverley Dungeon</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/w/Quest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Quest\">Quest</a></th><td colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/w/Scorpion_Catcher\" title=\"Scorpion Catcher\">Scorpion Catcher</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/w/Choose_Option\" title=\"Choose Option\">Options</a></th><td colspan=\"12\">Pick-up</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"8\"><a href=\"/w/Examine\" title=\"Examine\">Examine</a></th><td colspan=\"12\">Looks vicious!</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Map</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-full-width-content infobox-image\"><a class=\"mw-kartographer-map mw-kartographer-container center\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 300px;background-image: url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-04-27_a/tiles/rendered/-1/-3/0_0_3.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-04-27_a/tiles/rendered/-1/-3/0_1_3.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-04-27_a/tiles/rendered/-1/-3/0_0_2.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-04-27_a/tiles/rendered/-1/-3/0_1_2.png); background-position: -200.625px -43.75px, 55.375px -43.75px, -200.625px 212.25px, 55.375px 212.25px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\" data-mw=\"interface\" data-style=\"0\" data-width=\"300\" data-height=\"300\" data-zoom=\"-3\" data-lat=\"6642\" data-lon=\"2805\" data-mapid=\"-1\" data-plane=\"0\" data-overlays=\"[&quot;pins&quot;]\" href=\"/w/Special:Map/-1/-3/-1/2805/6642\"></a></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Advanced data</th></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"8\">NPC ID</th><td colspan=\"12\">5228,5229,5230</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<p><b>Kharid Scorpions</b> are a rare species of <a href=\"/w/Scorpion\" title=\"Scorpion\">scorpion</a> native to the <a href=\"/w/Kharidian_Desert\" title=\"Kharidian Desert\">Kharidian Desert</a>. They play a prominent role in the <a href=\"/w/Scorpion_Catcher\" title=\"Scorpion Catcher\">Scorpion Catcher</a> <a href=\"/w/Quest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Quest\">quest</a>, during which players must capture three that escaped from the wizard <a href=\"/w/Thormac\" title=\"Thormac\">Thormac</a>. Players can catch them during the Scorpion Catcher with a <a href=\"/w/Scorpion_cage\" title=\"Scorpion cage\">scorpion cage</a>. Locations are as follows:\n</p>\n<ul><li>One roams freely on the <span class=\"floornumber\"><span class=\"floornumber-gb\">1<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">st</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"British convention; floor 2 in the US\">UK</span>&#93;</sup></span><span class=\"floornumber-us noexcerpt\">2<sup class=\"floornumber-ordinal-suffix\">nd</sup>&#160;floor<sup class=\"floornumber-help noexcerpt\">&#91;<span class=\"fact-text floor-convention\" title=\"US convention; floor 1 in the UK\">US</span>&#93;</sup></span></span> of the <a href=\"/w/Edgeville_Monastery\" title=\"Edgeville Monastery\">Edgeville Monastery</a>.</li>\n<li>Another can be found in the beginning of the <a href=\"/w/Taverley_Dungeon\" title=\"Taverley Dungeon\">Taverley Dungeon</a>. The scorpion in Taverley Dungeon is behind a disguised wall that can only be opened after starting the quest.</li>\n<li>The final one is found in the Barbarian Agility area at the <a href=\"/w/Barbarian_Outpost\" title=\"Barbarian Outpost\">Barbarian Outpost</a>.</li></ul>\n<p>None of these scorpions are attackable. If players attempt to pick them up, they will always suffer 3 <a href=\"/w/Hitpoints\" title=\"Hitpoints\">Hitpoints</a> of typeless damage. This damage <b>can</b> kill the player if they have 3 HP or less when attempting to pick one up. The scorpion damage is not poisonous, though it is typeless (similar to damage from failing to pickpocket) and therefore unaffected by <a href=\"/w/Protection_prayers\" title=\"Protection prayers\">protection prayers</a>. Some players may use them as a form of suicide when they have low Hitpoints or are in need of stat healing.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Changes\">Changes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Kharid_Scorpion?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Kharid_Scorpion?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery_(historical)\">Gallery (historical)</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Kharid_Scorpion?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Gallery (historical)\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Kharid_Scorpion?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Gallery (historical)\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"text-align: center\" cellpadding=\"15\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:Kharid_Scorpion_(historical).png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Kharid Scorpion (historical).png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Kharid_Scorpion_%28historical%29.png/226px-Kharid_Scorpion_%28historical%29.png?4e497\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"226\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Kharid_Scorpion_%28historical%29.png/338px-Kharid_Scorpion_%28historical%29.png?4e497 1.5x, /images/thumb/Kharid_Scorpion_%28historical%29.png/451px-Kharid_Scorpion_%28historical%29.png?4e497 2x\" data-file-width=\"1570\" data-file-height=\"1045\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:Kharid_Scorpion.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Kharid Scorpion.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Kharid_Scorpion.png/170px-Kharid_Scorpion.png?a6456\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"170\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Kharid_Scorpion.png/255px-Kharid_Scorpion.png?a6456 1.5x, /images/thumb/Kharid_Scorpion.png/340px-Kharid_Scorpion.png?a6456 2x\" data-file-width=\"923\" data-file-height=\"815\" /></a></div></div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>29 March 2004 –<br />8 May 2007\n</td>\n<td>8 May 2007 –<br />present\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\