4\" data-file-height=\"122\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Barbarian_guard\" title=\"Barbarian guard\">Barbarian guard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Seer\" title=\"Seer\">Seer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Jailer\" title=\"Jailer\">Jailer</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kharid Scorpion</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Items</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Scorpion_cage\" title=\"Scorpion cage\"><img alt=\"Scorpion cage (empty).png\" src=\"/images/Scorpion_cage_%28empty%29.png?3f71e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"28\" height=\"24\" data-file-width=\"28\" data-file-height=\"24\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Scorpion_cage\" title=\"Scorpion cage\">Scorpion cage</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Related</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Scorpion_Catcher/Quick_guide\" title=\"Scorpion Catcher/Quick guide\">Quick Guide</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐7bfb498f95‐qlz7t\nCached time: 20220517124956\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.087 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.117 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 252/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 14019/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 430/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 845/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.038/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1286129/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   82.388      1 -total\n 56.75%   46.759      1 Template:Infobox_NPC\n 21.35%   17.587      1 Template:Scorpion_Catcher\n 15.07%   12.414      1 Template:Map\n 14.02%   11.551      1 Template:External\n 13.02%   10.727      1 Template:Navbox\n  7.35%    6.058      1 Template:FloorNumber\n  3.81%    3.143      1 Template:Ctg\n  1.85%    1.524      5 Template:Chatl\n  1.59%    1.311      1 Template:Plink\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:29918-0!canonical and timestamp 20220517124956 and revision id 14260998. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{External|rs|rsc}}\n{{Infobox NPC\n|name = Kharid Scorpion\n|image = [[File:Kharid Scorpion.png|250px]]\n|release = [[25 March]] [[2002]]\n|update = Latest RuneScape News (25 March 2002)\n|members = No\n|race = [[Scorpion]]\n|quest = [[Scorpion Catcher]]\n|location = [[Edgeville Monastery]], [[Barbarian Outpost]], [[Taverley Dungeon]]\n|options = Pick-up\n|examine = Looks vicious!\n|map = {{Map|name=Kharid Scorpion|2877,9796|2552,3570|3058,3488|mtype=pin|mapID=-1}}\n|id = 5228,5229,5230\n}}\n'''Kharid Scorpions''' are a rare species of [[scorpion]] native to the [[Kharidian Desert]]. They play a prominent role in the [[Scorpion Catcher]] [[quest]], during which players must capture three that escaped from the wizard [[Thormac]]. Players can catch them during the Scorpion Catcher with a [[scorpion cage]]. Locations are as follows:\n*One roams freely on the {{FloorNumber|uk=1}} of the [[Edgeville Monastery]].\n*Another can be found in the beginning of the [[Taverley Dungeon]]. The scorpion in Taverley Dungeon is behind a disguised wall that can only be opened after starting the quest.\n*The final one is found in the Barbarian Agility area at the [[Barbarian Outpost]].\n\nNone of these scorpions are attackable. If players attempt to pick them up, they will always suffer 3 [[Hitpoints]] of typeless damage. This damage '''can''' kill the player if they have 3 HP or less when attempting to pick one up. The scorpion damage is not poisonous, though it is typeless (similar to damage from failing to pickpocket) and therefore unaffected by [[protection prayers]]. Some players may use them as a form of suicide when they have low Hitpoints or are in need of stat healing.\n\n==Changes==\n\n===Gallery (historical)===\n{|style=\"text-align: center\" cellpadding=\"15\"\n|[[File:Kharid Scorpion (historical).png|center|300x150px]]\n|[[File:Kharid Scorpion.png|center|300x150px]]\n|-\n|29 March 2004 –<br/>8 May 2007\n|8 May 2007 –<br/>present\n|}\n\n{{Scorpion Catcher}}"}